**Code**:
Modify the method to initialize the logger *before* the app starts.

```csharp
using Serilog;

public static void Main(string[] args)
{
    // 1. Setup Logging Config
    Log.Logger = new LoggerConfiguration()
        .WriteTo.Console()
        .WriteTo.File("logs/healthcenter.txt", rollingInterval: RollingInterval.Day)
        .CreateLogger();

    try {
        Log.Information("Starting up Health Center App...");
        BuildAvaloniaApp().StartWithClassicDesktopLifetime(args);
    }
    catch (Exception ex) {
        Log.Fatal(ex, "Application start-up failed");
    }
    finally {
        Log.CloseAndFlush();
    }
}
```

